794
01:13:05,591 --> 01:13:06,931
Hi, honey.

795
01:13:07,885 --> 01:13:10,885
Grandma!

796
01:13:11,096 --> 01:13:12,636
Hello, Grandma.

797
01:13:12,848 --> 01:13:16,098
