891
01:20:46,218 --> 01:20:47,428
All right.

892
01:20:48,887 --> 01:20:51,387
It's all about timing.
Just be easy.

893
01:20:54,059 --> 01:20:55,389
Follow through.

894
01:21:00,065 --> 01:21:02,525
