issue a warrant for your arrest.

949
01:23:41,309 --> 01:23:42,729
He's my son.

950
01:23:43,353 --> 01:23:45,363
I'm not leaving
without him, Jack.

951
01:23:45,814 --> 01:23:47,024
Fine.

